# KNOUX Player X™ Developer SDK

Complete development kit for creating powerful plugins for KNOUX Player X.

## Features

- TypeScript support with full type definitions
- Plugin templates and scaffolding tools
- Build system with webpack integration
- Testing framework setup
- Documentation generation
- CLI tools for plugin development
- Example projects and best practices

## Installation

```bash
npm install @knoux/player-x-developer-sdk
```

## Quick Start

Create a new plugin:
```bash
npx knoux-plugin-cli create my-awesome-plugin
cd my-awesome-plugin
npm install
npm run dev
```

## Documentation

- [Getting Started Guide](docs/GETTING_STARTED.md)
- [API Reference](docs/API.md)
