## Requirements

- Node.js 16+
- npm 8+
- TypeScript 4.9+

## Building Plugins

```bash
# Development mode with hot reload
npm run plugin:dev

# Production build
npm run plugin:build

# Generate documentation
npm run docs
```

## CLI Commands

- `knoux-plugin-cli create <name>` - Create new plugin from template
- `knoux-plugin-cli build` - Build plugin for distribution
- `knoux-plugin-cli dev` - Start development server
- `knoux-plugin-cli test` - Run plugin tests

